<div class="big-container">
  <article class="article">
    <div style="width:fit-content;padding:10px; height:auto;background-color: rgb(0, 102, 255);border-radius: 10px;">
      <h3 style="text-align: center;color: #ffffff;">归档</h3>
    </div>
    <div class="topsign-title">
      <h2 class="topsign-text">文件归档</h2>
      <p style="color:var(--text-muted);">搜索文章 | 浏览论文 | 下载资料</p>
    </div>
    <script type="text/javascript" src="../js/comcode/com_artmenu.js"></script>
    <div class="sign-container" style="padding:15px;">
      <div class="search" style="margin-bottom:15px;">
        <input type="text" class="searchTerm" placeholder="搜索文章..." id="inpele" style="background:var(--bg-secondary);color:var(--text-primary);border:1px solid var(--border-light);">
        <button class="searchButton" onclick="{output()}" style="background:var(--text-link);color:#fff;"><i class="fa fa-search"></i></button>
      </div>
      <div style="text-align:center;margin-bottom:10px;">
        <button onclick="{searchmode = 1;document.getElementById('strict').style.color='var(--text-link)';document.getElementById('loose').style.color='var(--text-muted)';}" style="cursor:pointer;background:none;border:none;font-size:14px;padding:5px 10px;color:var(--text-link);" type="button" id="strict">严格搜索</button>
        <span style="color:var(--text-light);">|</span>
        <button onclick="{searchmode = 2;document.getElementById('loose').style.color='var(--text-link)';document.getElementById('strict').style.color='var(--text-muted)';}" style="cursor:pointer;background:none;border:none;font-size:14px;padding:5px 10px;color:var(--text-muted);" type="button" id="loose">宽泛搜索</button>
      </div>
      <div id="1">
        <div class="column-container-wider">
          <ul class="column_box" id="like-box">
            <script>print_content();</script>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div style="display:flex;gap:20px;margin-top:20px;">
      <div class="sign-container" style="flex:1;padding:15px;">
        <ul class="column_box" id="like-box">
          <li class="column-title">
            <span class="at-sort b-b-ece fl"><a class="at-sort-comment-a c-666 fl" style="font-family: Georgia, 'Times New Roman', Times, serif;">论文</a></span>
          </li>
          <li class="person-intro-detail">
            <details>
              <summary style="color:var(--text-primary);cursor:pointer;">简介</summary>
              <p style="color:var(--text-muted);">这里收录优秀论文，格式统一为PDF，字数>5000</p>
              <script>print_essays();</script>
            </details>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="sign-container" style="flex:1;padding:15px;">
        <ul class="column_box" id="like-box">
          <li class="column-title">
            <span class="at-sort b-b-ece fl"><a class="at-sort-comment-a c-666 fl" style="font-family: Georgia, 'Times New Roman', Times, serif;">资料</a></span>
          </li>
          <li class="person-intro-detail">
            <p style="color:var(--text-primary);line-height:2;">
              文件备案 历史资料 马恩列斯毛著作文选/全集和各时期著作[PDF]<br>
              <a href="https://www.aliyundrive.com/s/QXuNy5c7sQz">点此获取</a><br>
              文件备案 历史资料 《红旗》1958-1976 汇总[PDF]<br>
              <a href="https://www.aliyundrive.com/s/4LuDRBQxLT8">点此获取</a><br>
              文件备案 历史资料 千禧年后社会调研分析报告[PDF]<br>
              <a href="https://www.aliyundrive.com/s/aJvXeStg1wK">点此获取</a>
            </p>
            <p style="text-align:right;color:var(--text-light);font-size:12px;">基于 Aliyundrive</p>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </article>
</div>